synthesis_method: Dissolve 0.111 g (0.343 mmol) of ZrOCl2·8H2O and 0.8377 g (6.86 mol) of benzoic acid in 20 mL DMF solvent. Add 0.057 g (0.343 mmol) of H2BDC, sonicate until dissolved, and heat the solution at 120 °C for 1 day.
